# The devcontainer image (.devcontainer/Dockerfile) copies ONLY the flake-eval
# inputs (flake.nix, flake.lock, treefmt.nix) — see its §3 pre-warm step. Ship
# nothing else to the daemon: the repo root holds a multi-GB nixbox.qcow2, a
# /nix store `result` symlink, and secrets/ that must never enter build context.
#
# Ignore everything, then re-include exactly what the Dockerfile needs.
*
!flake.nix
!flake.lock
!treefmt.nix
